OL,3,CHundreds of jobs set to go at wet wipe
OL,4,Cfactory in Flint
OL,6,FHundreds of jobs are set to be lost at
OL,7,Fa wet wipes manufacturer in Flintshire
OL,8,Fafter the company decided to move its
OL,9,Fproduction to Germany.
OL,11,FThe Kimberly-Clark plants in Flint,
OL,12,Fwhich produces wet wipes and toilet
OL,13,Froll, is due to close in 2025 with the
OL,14,Floss of around 250 jobs.
OL,16,FThe Unite union, which represents
OL,17,Fworkers, has described the decision as
OL,18,Fa "bombshell".
