OL,6,F"The consultation was initiated
OL,7,Ffollowing the government's decision to
OL,8,Fban all baby wipes containing plastic
OL,9,Fin the UK from mid-2026.
OL,11,F"While phasing out plastics from our
OL,12,Fbaby wipes is a key part of K-C's
OL,13,Fsustainability plans and we already
OL,14,Fsell plastic-free baby wipes in the
OL,15,FUK, it isn't possible to adapt our
OL,16,Fmanufacturing processes in Flint in
OL,17,Ftime, and it is therefore no longer
OL,18,Fviable to keep our consumer and B2B
OL,19,Fsites operational.
