OL,6,F"Decisions that involve our employees
OL,7,Fare the hardest to make and we know
OL,8,Fthis is a challenging period for our
OL,9,Fteam. Supporting them through this
OL,10,Fcomplex situation is our top priority.
OL,12,F"We will also continue to work closely
OL,13,Fwith our customers and retailers on
OL,14,Ftransition plans for baby wipes and
OL,15,Fprofessional tissues products in the
OL,16,FUK.
OL,18,F"We thank union and employee
OL,19,Frepresentatives for a constructive and
OL,20,Frespectful consultation process."
