OL,6,FUnite general secretary Sharon Graham
OL,7,Fsaid: "The closure of the two Kimberly
OL,8,FClark mills would be a catastrophic
OL,9,Fblow to the economy and local
OL,10,Fcommunities of Flint and north Wales
OL,11,Fas a whole.
OL,13,F"The company has dropped this
OL,14,Fbombshell on its workforce. Our
OL,15,Fmembers are devastated and the effect
OL,16,Fon the local area will be catastrophic.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/8
