OL,6,F"Kimberly-Clark will reap millions in
OL,7,Fprofit from this move and our members
OL,8,Fwill struggle to now put food on the
OL,9,Ftable. Unite will fight to reverse
OL,10,Fthis decision and calls upon the
OL,11,Fgovernment to intervene to try and
OL,12,Fsave these vital jobs. This decision,
OL,13,Ftaken so rashly, cannot be accepted."
OL,15,FAlyn and Deeside's Labour MP Mark Tami
OL,16,Fsaid he was devastated for the 200-
OL,17,Fplus workers affected and their
OL,18,Ffamilies.
