OL,6,FHe said: "There is also a knock-on
OL,7,Feffect on a hundred or so workers at
OL,8,Fother companies in the supply chain
OL,9,Fwho service Kimberly-Clark, including
OL,10,FGXO, Deeside.
OL,12,F"I'm continuing to work with Unite and
OL,13,FWelsh Government to support those who
OL,14,Fare losing their jobs as much as
OL,15,Fpossible."
OL,17,FHe said Welsh Government cabinet
OL,18,Fsecretary Ken Skates' team had been in
OL,19,Fdiscussions with the firm and three
OL,20,Fcompanies interested in taking over
OL,21,Fthe site.
