OL,6,FMr Tami added: "The Welsh Government
OL,7,Fis ensuring that employees can access
OL,8,Fall relevant avenues of support
OL,9,Favailable and are supported into re-
OL,10,Femployment. Any constituents affected
OL,11,Fwho feel that I can help them should
OL,12,Fnot hesitate to contact my office."
OL,14,FThe company previously said most of
OL,15,Fits baby wipes "use a proprietary
OL,16,Ftechnology with 70% natural fibres and
OL,17,F30% plastic added to provide the
OL,18,Fnecessary strength to clean and care
OL,19,Ffor babies' skin properly".
